[gd_scene load_steps=3 format=3 uid="uid://b0embergrave_s2room01_chunk"]

; Cinder Vaults — Entry Hall base geometry (S2 default chunk visual).
; Hex-block placeholder geometry per §2 authoritative palette in
; team/uma-ux/palette-stratum-2.md. Reused as the shared base scene for
; multiple s2_*.tres chunk_defs (rooms 01 / 04 / 05 / 06 / 07 / 08) — the
; same way every s1_*.tres chunk_def references s1_room01_chunk.tscn. The
; chunk_def TRES carries the per-room mob_spawn + port differentiation;
; this scene is the shared floor + walls.
;
; Scholar-overlay distribution (§1.6 weighting) is decoration-tier
; authoring — applied per-zone in W3-T7 Stage 4 chunk_defs by varying
; mob_spawn density NOT by altering this base scene. Stage 4's contract is
; chunk-data + zone-wiring; future polish ticket re-skins this base scene
; with per-zone overlay props.
;
; Walls match the s1_room01_chunk pattern (4 StaticBody2D walls with
; RectangleShape2D collision) so MultiMobRoom + RoomGate physics behave
; identically across strata.

